  "description": "<p>之前我们报道过，19岁的《英雄联盟》玩家贾斯汀·卡特(Justin Carter)今年2月的时候，在《英雄联盟》游戏中对另外一个玩家说：“对，我就是疯了，我要找个都是小孩的学校，开枪干掉他们，然后生吃他们的心。” 随后他打出了“LOL(英语大笑的简写)”和“JK(开玩笑的简写)”，随后在今年2月14日被警察逮捕，罪名是恐怖主义恐吓。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e3a3e9f/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243591.htm&amp;t=%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BDLOL%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%B6%E5%85%A5%E7%8B%B1%E9%81%AD%E5%8F%97%E8%99%90%E5%BE%85+%E5%88%9B%E5%A4%A9%E4%BB%B7%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8A%E9%87%91\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243591.htm&amp;t=%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BDLOL%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%B6%E5%85%A5%E7%8B%B1%E9%81%AD%E5%8F%97%E8%99%90%E5%BE%85+%E5%88%9B%E5%A4%A9%E4%BB%B7%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8A%E9%87%91\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243591.htm&amp;t=%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BDLOL%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%B6%E5%85%A5%E7%8B%B1%E9%81%AD%E5%8F%97%E8%99%90%E5%BE%85+%E5%88%9B%E5%A4%A9%E4%BB%B7%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8A%E9%87%91\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243591.htm&amp;t=%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BDLOL%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%B6%E5%85%A5%E7%8B%B1%E9%81%AD%E5%8F%97%E8%99%90%E5%BE%85+%E5%88%9B%E5%A4%A9%E4%BB%B7%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8A%E9%87%91\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243591.htm&amp;t=%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BDLOL%E7%8E%A9%